123
00:06:46,833 --> 00:06:50,168
Welcome to the Men's Synchronized Swimming Team.

124
00:06:52,417 --> 00:06:53,085
I'm in Class 2.

125
00:06:53,462 --> 00:06:53,962
My surname is Wang.

126
00:06:54,168 --> 00:06:55,085
I'm Wang Zi.

127
00:06:55,708 --> 00:06:56,462
