128
00:06:56,502 --> 00:06:57,293
My surname is "Father."

129
00:06:57,417 --> 00:06:58,502
I'm "King Father."

130
00:07:02,917 --> 00:07:04,002
Isn't this a swimming team?

131
00:07:04,208 --> 00:07:05,377
