132
00:07:13,462 --> 00:07:14,293
Synchronized swimming

133
00:07:14,502 --> 00:07:16,333
is also known as water ballet.

134
00:07:17,042 --> 00:07:18,293
It originated in Europe.

135
00:07:18,542 --> 00:07:19,502
It started

136
00:07:19,502 --> 00:07:21,293
as a performance

137
00:07:21,293 --> 00:07:23,002
during the intervals of swimming competitions.

138
00:07:23,208 --> 00:07:25,002
It is highly artistic

139
00:07:25,042 --> 00:07:26,417
and requires certain techniques,

140
00:07:26,708 --> 00:07:28,377
along with dancing and strength basics.

141
00:07:28,833 --> 00:07:29,542
In general,

142
00:07:29,625 --> 00:07:30,962
synchronized swimming is divided into

143
00:07:31,002 --> 00:07:31,462
solo,

144
00:07:31,708 --> 00:07:32,293
duet,

145
00:07:32,625 --> 00:07:33,248
mixed duet,

146
00:07:33,417 --> 00:07:34,377
and team categories.

147
00:07:34,708 --> 00:07:36,708
Based on the Olympic standards and rules,

148
00:07:36,793 --> 00:07:39,042
