168
00:08:18,333 --> 00:08:19,002
What's wrong?

169
00:08:19,293 --> 00:08:21,208
A few boys doing synchronized swimming.

170
00:08:21,417 --> 00:08:22,542
Doesn't it feel strange?

171
00:08:22,793 --> 00:08:24,125
